LOS ANGELES : Negro Harry
Winston, long time leading Com
munist Party figure, has been
permitted to sue the US. govern
ment for negligence.


He seeks 81 million for the
loss of his eyesight, during his
prison confinement which ended
in 1861 on an clemency order
from the late Pre- sident Kennedy.

ficials did not give him adequate
physical attention. but he did
not charge them with any abusive
actions. He had complained of
recurring headaches.


The permission to sue the
federal government, markes the
first time an individual has been
allowed to file such action.
